    "   - Verify 'competitor' name is correct",
    "",
    "2. CUSTOMIZE SELECTORS (optional):",
    "   - Open the target website in your browser",
    "   - Right-click element â†’ Inspect",
    "   - Find CSS selectors for content, title, date, author",
    "   - Test in browser console: document.querySelector('your-selector')",
    "   - Update 'selectors' object with comma-separated fallbacks",
    "",
    "3. CONFIGURE CRAWL FREQUENCY:",
    "   - '6h'  = every 6 hours (changelogs, fast-moving competitors)",
    "   - '12h' = every 12 hours (blogs, moderate updates)",
    "   - '24h' = daily (pricing pages, news, slower sources)",
    "   - 'manual' = only crawl when triggered via MCP tool",
    "",
    "4. SET MAX PAGES:",
    "   - maxPages: limits how deep to crawl",
    "   - Use 1 for single pages (pricing)",
    "   - Use 5-10 for blogs/changelogs",
    "   - Use 2-3 for news aggregators",
    "",
    "5. ADD NEW SOURCES:",
