    "   - Choose appropriate 'type': blog | changelog | pricing | docs | news | forum",
    "",
    "=== FIELD REFERENCE ===",
    "name:             Unique identifier for this source",
    "url:              Starting URL to crawl",
    "type:             Content type (blog, changelog, pricing, docs, news, forum)",
    "competitor:       (optional) Competitor name for filtering in queries",
    "crawl_frequency:  How often to re-crawl (6h, 12h, 24h, manual)",
    "enabled:          Set to true to start crawling",
    "selectors:        (optional) CSS selectors - use commas for fallbacks",
    "tags:             Array of tags for categorization",
    "maxPages:         Maximum pages to crawl",
    "pagination:       (optional) How to follow to next page",
    "",
    "=== TIPS ===",
    "- Start with enabled: false and test one source at a time",
